gym_denki_015_receptionist_01:
You’ll see what the Gym Test is all about once
you go outside.
gym_denki_015_denki_00:
Ladies aaand gentlemens! It’s time for the
Iono Zone![npcn:2C]
gym_denki_015_denki_02:
Your eyeballs are MINE—caught in my
Electroweb! Whosawhatsit? Iono! I’m the Gym\r
Leader here! ’Ello, ’ello, hola! Ciao and bonjour![npcn:19]
gym_denki_015_denki_03a:
Indeedy-doo! I kick it as Gym Leader when I’m
not producin’ sweet content on the internet as an\r
influencer to bring dreams to the masses![npcn:19]
gym_denki_015_denki_03b:
Oh snap! Look at you—already a master of
Iono-ese! Not your first rodeo, then, eh?[npcn:19]
gym_denki_015_denki_03:
And, uh...I hope this doesn’t come as too much of
a surprise, but you’re bein’ broadcast live to the\r
world right now! Smile![npcn:19]
gym_denki_015_denki_04:
Anywho, challenger! Thanks for coming out to the
Levincia Gym to see me![npcn:19]
gym_denki_015_denki_05:
I’m super happy you’re here, but I’m also a bit of
a celeb, ya know? I’m all kiiinds of busy![npcn:19]
gym_denki_015_denki_06:
So I can’t collab with you unless I know you can
bring in those sweet, sweet viewer numb—\c
Er, I mean, I gotta make sure you can bring
some real passion to my stream! Nyohoho![npcn:19]
gym_denki_015_denki_07:
And! So! If you wanna battle me, you’re gonna
have to help me make this livestream a viral hit\r
first! Got it?[npcn:19]
gym_denki_015_denki_08:
I can tell you just can’t wait to get started! Well,
well, WELL then! Allow me to explain the plan![npcn:19]
gym_denki_015_head_teacher_01:
[BD06:0]Oh, [trnm:0]. What a
coincidence,\r
meeting\r
you here.[npcn:A]
gym_denki_015_denki_09:
Say whaaat?! D’you guys know each other
or somethin’?[npcn:19]
gym_denki_015_denki_17:
This here dude had a real aura about him when
he was walkin’ down the street, so I snatched him\r
up for my dealio here![npcn:19]
gym_denki_015_head_teacher_02: You are, er, too kind. Ha ha ha...[npcn:A]
gym_denki_015_denki_18:
Well anywho, [trnm:0]!\c
Since you’re today’s challenger, I’mma have you
play hide-and-seek with Mr. Walksabout here![npcn:19]
gym_denki_015_denki_10:
Look for the good gentleman using the street
surveillance cameras! Find ’im three times, and\r
you can consider this Gym Test passed![npcn:19]
gym_denki_015_denki_11:
We need a better name for this challenge,
though! I’ll call it...\c
“Where in Levincia Is Mr. Walksabout?”![npcn:19]
gym_denki_015_denki_12:
Y’think that title’s safe? There’s nothing iffy
about it or anything, right?[npcn:19]
gym_denki_015_denki_13:
Eh, whatevs! I ’unno ’bout you, but I’m ready to
go! Get ready to hide, Mr. Walksabout![npcn:19]
gym_denki_015_head_teacher_03:
I feel that I owe the Pokémon League for many
a past favor, so I am more than happy to help.\c
Do bear with me as I try my best in my
allocated role.[npcn:A]
